title: Project Momentum
description: This web application features an AI-powered scheduler that automatically organizes users' to-do lists, prioritizes tasks based on deadlines, preferences and personalized configurations.

title: MindMappers
description: A collaborative mind-mapping tool designed to facilitate real-time brainstorming and idea organization for individuals and teams.

title: D-TicketMaster

title: Magnify Access

title: PINTOS
description: Pintos is an educational operating system development project that provides hands-on experience with core OS components—such as processes, threads, scheduling, and file systems—using a simple hardware simulator.

description: A Android application that allows users to order food from their favourite restaurants and have it delivered to their doorstep.

title: Pacman
